- active repo on ci.framgia.vn
- authenticate reports at ci-reports.framgia.vn
- enable CW/email notification if neccessary
- create automated build on docker hub
- create Dockerfile and push to github repo
- create .drone.yml
- install python3
- pip3 install framgia-ci
- pip install --upgrade pip
- framgia-ci init ruby
- edit .framgia-ci.yml as your requirements
- commit and push to github, create PRs
